{"tid":897434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【馬凱被拒入境】張建宗：不要與香港新聞自由扯上關係","createTime":"2018-11-11T01:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T04:30:10.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"60cd2acd419d62ab42bd20cc7a187dc3633e46eb","tid":897434,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T01:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181111/s00001/02129ddda11ff02e68dc722612664ca8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181111%2Fs00001%2F02129ddda11ff02e68dc722612664ca8.jpg&h=26ba63d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《金融時報》亞洲新聞主編、外國記者會（FCC）第一副主席馬凱（Victor Mallet）繼被拒工作簽證續期後，日前以旅客身分入境亦被拒，引起關注。政務司長張建宗昨回應時稱，在報章上留意到有「一些人士」於入境方面有問題，但「不要與香港的新聞自由扯上關係」，重申入境處根據一貫政策和考慮因素決定，不會透露原因。<br />\n<br />\n至於異見作家馬建來港出席香港國際文學節講座，一度因為大館突然拒借場地而出現波折，張建宗指，「特區政府在這件事情上完全沒有參與」。"},{"pid":"3b1de82e83a318bacd459a091990717b720983b5","tid":897434,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T01:52:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181111/s00001/1541895751834\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181111%2Fs00001%2F1541895751834&d=w5dhjXZP8%2BCC%2Ft1jVEv2cNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=87156661\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181111%2Fs00001%2F1541895751834&h=3c75f07c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181111/s00001/1541895751834</a>"},{"pid":"26c21669389b3c3171a8edd54a2bdc11b0340998","tid":897434,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T02:03:10.000Z","msg":"咁又同咩有關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f85a703a5e74160e07973ed0ac04ea0e8f5d7c","tid":897434,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T02:04:19.000Z","msg":"以前話官字兩個口<br />\n依家直頭成個場既人都係佢既"},{"pid":"5fe5386d38caefeee6738e290c98f81960fb70d1","tid":897434,"uid":195516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T02:09:49.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得佢老細都準備炒佢；<br />\n唔理解英式教育出黎嘅點解可以做共狗做到如斯地步。"},{"pid":"2b09813fa660fe9c0b8b9a83aeeb5b45b88e8285","tid":897434,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T02:10:34.000Z","msg":"具香港特色既新聞自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2b7e32d39a3524169599502fa9c298cf5e18ae","tid":897434,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T02:11:33.000Z","msg":"凡係正苦出黎否認既，就係等於承認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300526b530d0753cf5b5826e7e4e0611e3128ccb","tid":897434,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T02:12:11.000Z","msg":"成個濕尻政府都擘大眼講大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e00407528e5d80359e5dd773f05629ba564bfe","tid":897434,"uid":23058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T02:13:27.000Z","msg":"講完有無面紅?"},{"pid":"661d6bcd6c4cbe0f2e70578713259b53df4d8736","tid":897434,"uid":192068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"300526b530d0753cf5b5826e7e4e0611e3128ccb","tid":897434,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T02:12:11.000Z","msg":"成個濕尻政府都擘大眼講大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T04:30:10.000Z","msg":"放個錄音機做官好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}